### 空间管理接口

@baseUrl = http://localhost

### 创建空间
POST {{baseUrl}}/space
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "测试空间",
  "description": "这是一个测试空间"
}

### 更新空间
PUT {{baseUrl}}/space/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "更新后的空间名称",
  "description": "更新后的描述"
}

### 删除空间
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/space/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 根据ID查询空间
GET {{baseUrl}}/space/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 查询空间列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/space/list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 分页查询空间
POST {{baseUrl}}/space/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "current": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "keyword": ""
}

### 根据用户ID查询空间
GET {{baseUrl}}/space/owner/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

